</p><p>+ Queue Job</p><p>php artisan queue:work --queue=import,export,reCalculate,runBatchTH,runBatchID --timeout=0</p><p>php artisan queue:work --queue=import,validate,convert,convert30 --timeout=0</p><p>======</p><p>chown www-data:www-data laravel-2023-03-01.log<br>=======<br>netsh wlan show profiles<br>netsh wlan show profile name="tên-WiFi" key=clear<br>========</p><p>Rút ngắn hàng ghi log lại<br>echo "$(tail -n 10000 thpm_query.log)" &gt;thpm_query.log</p><p>===== Xoa image<br>docker stop php-app-82</p><p>docker rm php-app-82</p><p>docker image ls</p><p>docker image rm 7fed8f1d90de</p><p>========== docker-compose.yum</p><p>cd /opt/gbm/</p><p>==== sshkey</p><p>-rw-rw-r-- 664 not working</p><p>-rw-r--r--. 644 working</p><p>#chmod 644 authorized_keys</p><p>Create sshKey nếu có user chuyển quyên user rùi tạo key</p><p>ssh-keygen -t rsa</p><p>#</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Add sshkey qua 1 serve #&nbsp;</p><p>#touch authorized_keys</p><p>#vi authorized_keys</p><p>cd .ssh ở tổng không cần vào /home/</p><p>#file_put_contents(/var/www/sm-new-real/backend/storage/framework/cache/data<br>chmod -R 777 framework/</p><p># docker inspect db | grep MYSQL_</p><p>$paths = @(<br>''HKLM:\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\*'',<br>''HKLM:\SOFTWARE\WOW6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\*'',<br>''HKCU:\Software\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\*''<br>)</p><p>$apps = $paths | ForEach-Object { Get-ItemProperty $_ } | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -ne $null }</p><p>$apps | Select-Object DisplayName, DisplayVersion, Publisher, InstallDate | Export-Csv -Path C:\installed.csv -NoTypeInformation</p><p>====</p><p>backup .ssh</p><p>cp -R .ssh ~<br>chmod 600 ~/.ssh/id_rsa<br></p><p>//php artisan tinker check redis</p><p>Queue::getRedis()-&gt;keys(''*'')</p><p>Queue::size(''release_to_thpm_eg_product_staging'');</p><p>php artisan queue:clear --queue=releaseStagingID<br>php artisan queue:clear redis --queue=emails<br>php artisan queue:retry --queue=name</p><p>/